		<title>Advanced Installation Options</title>
		<partintro>
			<para>
				This part of the <citetitle>Fedora Installation Guide</citetitle> covers more advanced topics, which will be useful to users who need to perform a non-standard installation. It contains information about custom boot options, automating the installation using Kickstart, booting from a network location instead of local media, etc.
			</para>
